==English==

===Alternative forms===
* [[flash bang]]
* [[flashbang]]

===Etymology===
{{compound|lang=en|flash|bang}}. From the bright flash of light and loud bang (a concussive shockwave of sound) generated by this hand-throwable man-portable explosive device.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A hand [[grenade]] that produces a very bright flash and a loud [[explosion]], but no [[shrapnel]] and minimal explosive force, to disorient the target.

====Synonyms====
* [[flash grenade]]
* [[stun grenade]]
* [[concussion grenade]]

